###########
## PaRSS ##
###########

MODULE DEPENDENCIES:
 - Link:                  http://drupal.org/project/link
 - Libraries API:         http://drupal.org/project/libraries

3RD PARTY LIBRARIES
 - PaRSS jQuery Library:  http://nicksantamaria.net/article/rehosting-parss-jquery-library
                          (Rehosted due to plugins.jquery.com being out of service)

INSTALLATION:
 1. Download this module and all it's dependencies
 2. Enable module and dependencies as-per normal
 3. Download the PaRSS jQuery library to sites/all/libraries/parss
 4. Ensure the following filepath is valid:
     sites/all/libraries/parss/jquery.parss.uncompressed.js

CONFIGURATION:
 1. Add and configure some link fields using link.module
 2. Go to the display settings for that field
 3. Change the formatter to "PaRSS"
 4. Adjust the configuration of the formatter by clicking the cog. 
    Settings include:
     - Number of rows from the RSS feed to display
     - List type to use (ul / ol)
     - Date format options
     - Show descriptions?
 5. Click "Update"
